---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Refund Policy | Gus Digital Solutions">
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-dark-900 min-h-screen">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl prose prose-invert prose-lg">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-dark-400 text-sm mb-12">Last Updated: January 26, 2026</p>

      <div class="bg-primary-900/20 border border-primary-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-primary-400 mt-0">100% Satisfaction Guarantee</h2>
        <p class="mb-0">
          We stand behind our services. If you are not completely satisfied with our work within the first 30 days, we will work with you to make it right or provide a full refund.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2>1. Service Refunds</h2>
      <p>
        For all service-based projects (Website builds, SEO audits, Automation setups), we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Eligibility:</strong> You must request a refund within 30 days of the initial payment or project start date.</li>
        <li><strong>Process:</strong> Simply email us at <a href="mailto:gus@gusdigitalsolutions.com">gus@gusdigitalsolutions.com</a> with your request. No complex forms or questions asked.</li>
        <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> Refunds are processed within 5-10 business days.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Digital Products</h2>
      <p>
        For downloadable digital goods (Templates, E-books), due to the nature of the product, all sales are generally final. However, if you find the file defective or corrupt, please contact us for a replacement or store credit.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Cancellations</h2>
      <p>
        You may cancel ongoing monthly services (like maintenance or SEO retainers) at any time. Cancellations will take effect at the end of the current billing cycle.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any refund requests or questions, please contact us directly:
        <br/><br/>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:gus@gusdigitalsolutions.com" class="text-primary-400">gus@gusdigitalsolutions.com</a><br/>
        <strong>Response Time:</strong> We aim to respond to all inquiries within 1 business day.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
